content:

title: Bain Warns Tech Services Firms: AI And Global Shifts Could Slash Revenues By 30%
description: The global technology services industry faces disruption, with artificial intelligence emerging as the biggest game-changer, according to Bain & Company’s latest report, The New Growth Equation for Tech Services.
